TVB-UrSh HVLK BThMV M'yQSh ShPhThYV VHV'a KSYL.
GM BL'a-D'yTh NPhSh L'a-TVB V'aTSh BUrGLYM ChVT'a.
'aVLTh 'aDM ThSLPh DUrKV V'yL-YHVH YZ'yPh LBV.
HVN YSYPh Ur'yYM UrBYM VDL MUr'yHV YPhUrD.
'yD ShQUrYM L'a YNQH VYPhYCh KZBYM L'a YMLT.
UrBYM YChLV PhNY-NDYB VKL-HUr'y L'aYSh MThN.
KL 'aChY-UrSh ShN'aHV 'aPh KY MUr'yHV UrChQV MMNV MUrDPh 'aMUrYM L'a-HMH.
QNH-LB 'aHB NPhShV ShMUr ThBVNH LMTSh'a-TVB.
'yD ShQUrYM L'a YNQH VYPhYCh KZBYM Y'aBD.
L'a-N'aVH LKSYL Th'yNVG 'aPh KY-L'yBD MShL BShUrYM.
ShKL 'aDM H'aUrYK 'aPhV VThPh'aUrThV 'yBUr 'yL-PhSh'y.
NHM KKPhYUr Z'yPh MLK VKTL 'yL-'yShB UrTShVNV.
HVTh L'aBYV BN KSYL VDLPh TUrD MDYNY 'aShH.
BYTh VHVN NChLTh 'aBVTh VMYHVH 'aShH MShKLTh.
'yTShLH ThPhYL ThUrDMH VNPhSh UrMYH ThUr'yB.
ShMUr MTShVH ShMUr NPhShV BVZH DUrKYV YVMTh.
MLVH YHVH ChVNN DL VGMLV YShLM-LV.
YSUr BNK KY-YSh ThQVH V'aL-HMYThV 'aL-ThSh'a NPhShK.
GUrL-ChMH NSh'a 'yNSh KY 'aM-ThTShYL V'yVD ThVSPh.
ShM'y 'yTShH VQBL MVSUr LM'yN ThChKM B'aChUrYThK.
UrBVTh MChShBVTh BLB-'aYSh V'yTShTh YHVH HY'a ThQVM.
Th'aVTh 'aDM ChSDV VTVB-UrSh M'aYSh KZB.
YUr'aTh YHVH LChYYM VShB'y YLYN BL-YPhQD Ur'y.
TMN 'yTShL YDV BTShLChTh GM-'aL-PhYHV L'a YShYBNH.
LTSh ThKH VPhThY Y'yUrM VHVKYCh LNBVN YBYN D'yTh.
MShDD-'aB YBUrYCh 'aM BN MBYSh VMChPhYUr.
ChDL-BNY LShM'y MVSUr LShGVTh M'aMUrY-D'yTh.
'yD BLY'yL YLYTSh MShPhT VPhY UrSh'yYM YBL'y-'aVN.
NKVNV LLTShYM ShPhTYM VMHLMVTh LGV KSYLYM.
